Series following a tough Australian who rescues orphan joeys and raises his brood of almost thirty kangaroos at an outback sanctuary near Alice Springs.


1/6 Brolga provides two orphan joeys with everything they need, including a makeshift pouch.

2/6 It is a busy week as Brolga has to deal with toilet training and a bad-tempered kangaroo.

3/6 Brolga discovers that one of his kangaroos has had a baby and teaches Rex and Ruby to hop.

4/6 Brolga lets the joeys out for a night-time hop and there is drama at dinner time for Ruby.

5/6 As winter draws in at the sanctuary, Brolga makes a life-changing decision.

6/6 Rex, Ruby, and latest orphan Bluey meet the rest of the mob for the first time.
